        <mxCell id="K27wWC6wkN7WmZvC_m9p-11" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Original design flaws:&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;- All knowledge is written into context of each agent -&amp;gt; not scalable, bloats the context&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- agent copies policies into memories - subject of drift/hallucinations&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Single read/write storage for every type of insight&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;- Agents operate on memories written by other agents - propt to injections&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
